snippet: Ryan Palmer parred his final hole at dusk for a seven-under-par 64 and the lead in the suspended first round of the Phoenix Open in Scottsdale, Ariz.
abstract: Ryan Palmer holds the lead in the first round of the Phoenix Open golf tournament, which was suspended due to darkness after a late start due to frost.
lead_paragraph: Ryan Palmer parred his final hole at dusk for a seven-under-par 64 and the lead in the suspended first round of the Phoenix Open in Scottsdale, Ariz.
